OL,4,Chuge piles of waste on land near homes
OL,6,FTwo men have been prosecuted over
OL,7,Fillegal waste activities in Preston
OL,8,Fwhich saw huge piles of household and
OL,9,Fcommercial rubbish dumped on land near
OL,10,Fhomes.
OL,12,FJamil Hanif, 49, and Richard Allen,
OL,13,F39, were taken to court by the
OL,14,FEnvironment Agency over their actions
OL,15,Fat a site on the east of Skeffington
OL,16,FRoad.
OL,18,FThe pair pleaded guilty to operating a
OL,19,Fregulated waste facility without the
OL,20,Fnecessary environmental permit between
OL,21,FNovember 2021 and December 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
