OL,6,FAllen also pleaded guilty to illegally
OL,7,Fdepositing controlled waste on the
OL,8,Fsame site between August 2022 and
OL,9,FJanuary 2023, in violation of
OL,10,Fenvironmental regulations.
OL,12,FEnvironment Agency bosses said the
OL,13,Fcase concerned a site owned by Preston
OL,14,FCity Council, which was initially
OL,15,Fleased to Finney Skeffington Ltd
OL,16,F(FSL), a company directed by Hanif.
