OL,4,Chuge piles of waste on land near homes
OL,6,FDespite the company's official dormant
OL,7,Fstatus, Hanif used the site for waste
OL,8,Fstorage and sorting activities related
OL,9,Fto house clearances linked to his
OL,10,Fwife's property rental business.
OL,11,FAllen, acting under Hanif's
OL,12,Finstructions, was responsible for
OL,13,Ftipping waste at the site.
