OL,3,CPair ran illegal tip site that dumped
OL,4,Chuge piles of waste on land near homes
OL,6,FIllegal waste activities at the site
OL,7,Ffirst came to light in November 2021,
OL,8,Fwhen a surveyor appointed by Preston
OL,9,FCity Council documented significant
OL,10,Fwaste accumulation, including
OL,11,Fhousehold and commercial waste,
OL,12,Fconstruction debris, and car parts. As
OL,13,Fa result, the council terminated FSL's
OL,14,Flease; however, Hanif continued to use
OL,15,Fthe site under a temporary agreement
OL,16,Fwith the council.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
