OL,3,CPair ran illegal tip site that dumped
OL,4,Chuge piles of waste on land near homes
OL,6,FFurther reports from local residents,
OL,7,Fincluding photographic and video
OL,8,Fevidence, showed waste being regularly
OL,9,Fdelivered and dumped on the site, with
OL,10,FAllen visibly involved in tipping
OL,11,Fwaste. This evidence, along with
OL,12,FEnvironment Agency investigations, led
OL,13,Fto the prosecution.
OL,15,FBoth defendants appeared before
OL,16,FBlackburn Magistrates Court on 29
OL,17,FJanuary and received 12-month
OL,18,Fcommunity orders, requiring them to
OL,19,Fcomplete 120 hours of unpaid work.
