OL,6,FAllen was ordered to pay a #300
OL,7,Fcontribution to prosecution costs and
OL,8,Fa #114 government surcharge and Hanif
OL,9,Fwas ordered to pay a #1,000
OL,10,Fcontribution to prosecution costs and
OL,11,Fa #114 government surcharge.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for the Environment
OL,14,FAgency said: "This case highlights our
OL,15,Fcommitment to tackling environmental
OL,16,Fcrime. Illegal waste operations pose
OL,17,Fsignificant risks to the environment
OL,18,Fand legitimate businesses.
